+		"               /*COLORKEY: bit31~0 ARGB data*/ \n"
+		"               eg:-colorkey [crtc_id:-1/-1/0xff0000ff/-1]\n"
+		"  -zpos        Set zpos for planes(0~3), if lower than 0,\n"
